data.description: SUPER LOW 2.375% Assumable VA loan and you don't have to be a VET to assume the loan!!! Welcome to 520 Hacienda Dr in the highly coveted Bradoaks area of NE Monrovia that is adjacent to the prestigious City of Bradbury (5 houses from the border)! Convenient location is only 1.4 miles to Old Town Monrovia w/its delicious restaurants, quaint shops, Friday night Family festivals, 1.3 miles to top rated California School of the Arts-San Gabriel Valley (charter high school), 1.5 miles to City of Hope, 1.2 miles to 210 Fwy, 2.2 miles to Gold Line. 2.375% Assumable VA Loan!! This Great Big Home has just been remodeled and renovated with new quartz countertops in kitchen and 2 bathrooms, exterior and interior paint, vinyl plank flooring and re-imagined backyard with fresh sod grass!!! 5 large bedrooms, 3.75 baths with two primary suites with one downstairs and one upstairs that's perfect for large multi-gen families! The downstairs primary bedroom has sliding glass door that opens to the newly redone backyard and could possibly be turned into an ADU on it's own or combined with the adjacent other downstairs bedroom to create big self contained living unit (check w/the city). Charming front bay window and fireplace grace the good sized living room, kitchen with freshly painted cabinets and new quartz countertops with breakfast bar that is perfect for entertaining because it is open to adjacent large dining/family room area. There is also an oversized walk in pantry, ceiling fans in all bedrooms & common areas, separate laundry room, multiple hallway closets for additional storage! Upstairs, you will find another primary bedroom suite with two closets, large covered balcony, good sized built-in sauna, bathroom with clawfoot soaking tub! Two additional roomy bedrooms and remodeled hall bathroom upstairs. The newly re-done backyard with freshly planted sod grass with sprinklers and rose bushes has plenty of room for a swing set, trampoline or perhaps adding a pool and spa. There is a large covered patio with built-in countertops that is perfect for barbequing and creating wonderful memories with family and friends for years to come! The home also includes owned solar panels as well! We almost forgot there is multi-purpose room off the kitchen that is perfect for home office, playroom, or mini gym? Last but not least, there is a large finished shed (approx 11x16) w/windows, laminate flooring, electrical & window AC that could be man cave, she shed, home office or ?
